channel.title: Server status problem
channel.description:
Hey, I finally got my server all ready to go so I went to the moparscape status checker. I filled in all the stuff and pressed ok. Then it says my server is offline and needs to be online to register.....ugh....
My server is online and i dont use a router so I dont need to portforward, I think. My server is honorspk.no-ip.biz can someone tell me how to fix the server status problem, also can someone go on my server and tell me if you can get on to prove that it's working?
Thanks.

item.dc:creator: @Torax Torax
item.description:

Check 123

  1. Your server is running
  2. You entered the right ip address in mopar
  3. You’re on the same computer that your server runs

Other than that I dont know what to tell you.
